list.abstract: row，英文单词，作名词、动词，翻译为行、排、划船、街道、吵闹等。

yingyinNormal.en: Row, row, row your boat, gently down the creek. If you see a big bad wolf, don't forget to shriek.
yingyinNormal.zh: 划，划，划你的船，在小河里轻轻的划。如果你看见一只大灰狼，不要忘记尖叫。

yingyinNormal.en: The silica is built into row upon row of tiny daggers along the leaf.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种硅物质组成了叶片边缘，鳞次栉比的小小利齿。

yingyinNormal.en: Row, row, row your boat, gently down the stream. If you see a crocodile, don't forget to scream. Picnic spot. Everybody off. Thank you Grampy Rabbit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 划，划，划你的船，在河流里轻轻的划。如果你看见一个鳄鱼，不要忘记了大叫哇！野餐区，大家下船。谢谢兔爷爷。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, geez, I don't know if I can ditch Priya two nights in a row.
yingyinNormal.zh: 完了，我不知道能不能连续两晚都放普丽娅鸽子。

yingyinNormal.en: They had to row away for the suction but now they'll be coming back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们必须划开才不会被吸下去，但现在可以回来了。

yingyinNormal.en: I had a chance to stop her too. Yeah? Who loses 57 coin tosses in a row?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我本来有机会阻止她的, 是吗？没想到猜钢崩儿我会连输47次。

yingyinNormal.en: November was the tenth month in a row we've added more than 200,000 jobs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 11月份是我们连续的第10个月份每月增加200,000以上的就业岗位。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, she didn't want to hang out with you guys two nights in a row. I'm so sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她不想连续应酬你们两晚，对不起。

yingyinNormal.en: Students. Yeah, we were sitting in the front row, and we kept looking at each other.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他学生。当时我们坐在第一排，一直眉来眼去的。

yingyinNormal.en: A player makes a bunch of shots in a row. People are sure they're gonna make the next one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 运动员连续投球命中，人们确信他们会投中下一个。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, how about tomorrow night we see a movie? You guys are going out two nights in a row?
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，我们明天晚上去看个电影如何？你们要连续两晚出去吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Seedy bar on the wrong side of the tracks, picnic near a lunatic asylum, a wine tasting on Skid Row.
yingyinNormal.zh: 去贫民区破旧的酒吧，去疯人院附近野餐，去贫民窟品酒。

yingyinNormal.en: He was stringing together, Like, three crossover moves in a row. Like, things he's never done before.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他连着做了三个胯下运球，过去他从未这样做过

yingyinNormal.en: No disrespect, I just lost in five for the second year in a row. Get her a bowling ball for all I care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恕我冒昧，我刚连输了五场，新赛季马上就要开始了，送她个保龄球，也不关我事。

yingyinNormal.en: You knew this and you didn't warn them? Little girl, you can go to a pretty dark place when you on death row.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么不警告他们？小女孩，天晓得我被折磨到想报仇的心有多可怕。

yingyinNormal.en: Everybody, listen up. We have a new student joining us today. His name is Mason, he's sitting in the back row.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都听着，今天我们有新同学加入，他叫梅森，坐在后面一排。

yingyinNormal.en: Doesn't explain why you gave up your hobbies. First prize, regional under tens' gymnastics, two years in a row.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你连续两年蝉联地区举办的十岁以下儿童体操比赛第一名。

yingyinNormal.en: First row are your musks. Second is woods, leathers and botanicals. Third is assorted pheromones. Tread lightly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一排是你要的麝香型，第二排是木头，皮革和植物味，第三排是配套的外激素，慎用。

yingyinNormal.en: Honey, you can't make people like each other. Not true. Leonard made me like you. And let me tell you, that was a hard row to hoe. Cheers, pal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，你不能逼别人互相喜欢。非也，莱纳德让我喜欢你，不瞒你说，这事可不容易啊，干杯吧，姐们。

examination_example.sentence: And for a long time—nearly seven years—<highlight>rowing</highlight> boats in the park has always been the first thing on my lists.
